{"tid":2007891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議大家盡可能都帶豬嘴出街","createTime":"2020-05-08T15:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T08:36:44.000Z","uid":350653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3591e1c558218cd6be7110caec557925ef553a6f","tid":2007891,"uid":350653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"1:可以更有效保護自己，減少傳播或被傳染既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2:試諗下個個出街都帶豬嘴，呢個時勢政府又唔可以干預我地帶豬嘴呢個行為。唔通佢地覺得呢個派既垃圾口罩效果比豬嘴好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設勇武之後出黎做野，都唔洗刻意棄豬嘴，可以減輕佢地既壓力，之前未有武漢肺炎果陣只要你身上有豬嘴就已經可以拉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且和理非同街坊又可以保護到勇武既手足，（因為到時個個都帶豬嘴，班狗根本分唔到），令佢地捉人難上加難 。就算班狗亂捉要鋤你都鋤唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由今日起，全民豬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6eaacc56e79a6497471810f1ce22d2ffa4ac04","tid":2007891,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"第一個post就post啲過期野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6962e0d1597c4efe57422ce4fe5bc5fc643006","tid":2007891,"uid":350653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc6eaacc56e79a6497471810f1ce22d2ffa4ac04","tid":2007891,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"第一個post就post啲過期野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"你估場疫症依加日日0確診就會好快完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實早前見到有人已經po過，不過沉哂底搵唔番再推多次姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806c2ebf0415e9f0811364f47337a351